column2: Top names for baby boys in England and Wales, 2009
These rankings have been produced using the exact spelling of the name given at birth registration. Similar names with different spellings have been counted separately.
Births where the name was not stated have been excluded from these figures. Of the 362,135 baby boys in the 2009 dataset, 12 were excluded for this reason.
Names with a count of 2 or less have been redacted using S40 of the Freedom of Information Act in order to protect the confidentiality of individuals.
